2.0.0.readme:
# lodash._slice v2.0.0

The internal Lo-Dash function `slice` as a Node.js module generated by lodash-cli.

## Dive in

There’s plenty of [documentation](http://lodash.com/docs), [unit tests](http://lodash.com/tests), & [benchmarks](http://lodash.com/benchmarks).

## Support

lodash._slice has been tested in at least Node.js 0.6.8-0.10.18.
